Blending the old with the new, Metal Gear Solid Delta potentially offers the best way to play Hideo Kojima's stealth-action classic. The Unreal Engine 5 driven visuals are standout, but it's clear that Konami has not optimised for 60fps strictly here; both base PS5 in and PS5 Pro waver between 40-60fps, with drops to 30 possible as well - with Pro hardware often coming out worse in comparison.
